   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...West winds 10 to 15 kt with gusts up to 20 kt and waves 2
to 3 ft. Locally higher waves to 4 ft are possible.

* WHERE...Port Wing to Sand Island WI, Sand Island to Bayfield
WI and Outer Apostle Islands Beyond 5 NM from Mainland.

* WHEN...Until 10 PM CDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Recreational boaters will experience
dangerous wave conditions and short wave periods. Waves will be
chaotic around cliffs and can double in size in the rebound
zone.</Snippet>
