   <name>Small Craft Advisory issued September 6 at 9:55AM EDT until September 7 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Cleveland OH</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...West winds 10 to 20 knots and waves 3 to 5 feet
expected.

* WHERE...The nearshore waters of Lake Erie from Vermilion OH to
Ripley NY.

* WHEN...From 1 PM this afternoon to 8 PM EDT Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
